{
  "stem": "5799.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe not a big one, but anybody, I said, anybody who even dared at the grave to speak a Nazi in the face was a hero.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Any one of those martyrs who did something was a hero.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they are unsung heroes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it-- it was-- it was packed with many people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my younger daughter came with my grandson.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know what he expected, but he looks like he didn't expect to be right-- it-- right in the middle of-- of slum New Haven.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But he [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you actively involved in Holocaust organizations?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am connected with the-- I was sick for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm just now getting back being active.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm connected with Ramapo College in-- Ramapo College Holocaust Center.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, everything, yearly, goes to Washington, to the museum.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And wherever there is a Holocaust Center, wherever's-- to the Anti-Defamation League, they have the Hidden Child, the hidden children that survived, I participate there too.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So wherever-- a little bit goes everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm active in ORT, because it teaches a profession.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I am active in Hadassah, because it has a hospital and helps the sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And most of all, I go as often as I can to Israel, because my friends went there and built it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And now, there are three generations of graves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And out of guilt, maybe, but I go there, because we are less and less, just to spend some time with those who are left.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I bring them here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They came to my-- our-- the weddings of the children, to the bar mitzvahs of the grandchildren, to our 50th anniversary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's a very close family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And thank God that there was a Jewish Brigade.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
